com.dsverdlo.AMuRate.objects

Class Track

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dsverdlo.AMuRate.objects.Track

  • public class Track
extends java.lang.Object
    Track abstract data type. Stores all kind of information of tracks. Since the JSON representation of a track returned by the api differs, the appropriate loadFromX method must be used when loading in data. The class implements Parcelable so it can be passed from one Activity to another.
    Author:
    david
